#The oxflower17 dataset consists of 1360 colour images (224 pixels high and 224 pixes width) of flowers in 17 classes, with 80 images per class. All images will be used for training. Before running the model, it will be indicated the ratio of samples that will be used for validation.


#The 17 classes are:
 
#| 0 | Daffodil
#| 1 | Snowdrop
#| 2 | Daisy  
#| 3 | ColtsFoot										
#| 4 | Dandelion										
#| 5 | Cowslip
#| 6 | Buttercup   
#| 7 | Windflower										
#| 8 | Pansy								
#| 9 | LilyValley										
#|10 | Bluebell 										
#|11 | Crocus
#|12 | Iris										
#|13 | Tigerlily										
#|14 | Tulip										
#|15 | Fritillary
#|16 | Sunflower

In [119]:
from tensorflow.keras.layers import Conv2D, MaxPooling2D, Flatten, Dense

model = tf.keras.models.Sequential()
model.add(Conv2D(32,(3,3),activation= 'relu', input_shape=(224,224,3)))
model.add(MaxPooling2D(2,2))
model.add(Conv2D(64,(5,5),activation= 'relu'))
model.add(MaxPooling2D(2,2))
model.add(Flatten())
model.add(Dense(n_classes,activation= 'softmax'))

main_window= tk.Tk()
main_window.title('Classifier GUI'.center(110))
main_window.geometry("600x250")



# importing data 
Name= ttk. Label(main_window,text = "Step 1: File Name")
Name.grid(row=0, column=0)

Name_var=tk.StringVar()
Name_entrybox= ttk.Entry(main_window, width = 16, textvariable= Name_var)
Name_entrybox.grid(row=0, column=1)

def Import_data():
    global DB
    Df_Name= Name_var.get()
    DB=cv2.imread(Df_Name)
    X_validate_img = cv2.resize(DB,(128,128))
    Confirmation ="Done"
    Confirmation_box=ttk.Entry(main_window, width=16)
    Confirmation_box.grid(row=0, column=3)
    Confirmation_box.insert(1, str(Confirmation))

Import_DataButton=ttk.Button(main_window, text='Import Data', command = Import_data).grid(row=0, column=2)



Name= ttk. Label(main_window,text = "Image Classifier")
Name.grid(row=1, column=0)

def Predict():
    from tensorflow.keras.models import load_model
    model_cnn = load_model('finalized_model.h5')
    a = DB
    X_validate_img = cv2.resize(a,(128,128))
    X_validate_std = X_validate_img/255.0
    X_validate_std.shape = (1, 128, 128, 3)
    y_pred = model_cnn.predict(X_validate_std)
    max_value = max(y_pred)
    max_index = number_list. index(max_value)
    if (max_index == 0):
        Confirmation ="Daffodil"
